data.description: Very charming 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom with 2 living rooms. One is very spacious, the other one is very comfortable with a gas fireplace. Kitchen has Granite countertops. Enjoy sitting outside on the full length deck out back. Sellers to offer $2,500 towards Buyer's closing costs with an acceptable offer. Call today to set up your private showing!
